name: PETRO PENGUINS
description: Petro Penguins ($PENGO) — a community-driven movement flipping the oil market through purpose, humor, and blockchain. From oil to optimism — the Penguins rise. The oil rigs that drilled and spilled Pengo’s world. The uprising begins where the damage began — the rigs. For decades, they drilled the oceans, spilled their greed, and scarred the homes of millions of penguins. Petro Penguins is a community-driven meme and art project created to inspire change through humor, storytelling, and digital creativity.
